### 🛒 5. Shop
 * *Direct link to the storefront.*
 * Features a tiny visual New or Live badge. Links directly to your merchandise lines (Copper bottles, T-shirts, Journals, Exercise books).
### 📞 6. Contact
 * *Direct link to communication channels, form endpoints, and local offices.*
